law.text: Any person violating any provision of this chapter shall be fined not less than one hundred dollars ($100) nor more than one thousand dollars ($1,000), or imprisoned for not more than six (6) months, or both.
law.history: Amended 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 14, effective July 15, 2002. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 78, sec. 22, effective July 15, 1986.
